==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Quenchless
<hw>Quench"less</hw>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Incapable of being quenched;
inextinguishable; <as>as, <ex>quenchless</ex> fire or fury</as>.</def>
⟦ldquo⟧Once kindled, <xex>quenchless</xex> evermore.⟦rdquo⟧
<rj><au>Byron.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><syn><b>Syn.</b> -- Inextinguishable; unquenchable.</syn>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p>-- <wordforms><wf>Quench"less*ly</wf>, <pos>adv.</pos> --
<wf>Quench"less*ness</wf>, <pos>n.</pos></wordforms>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Quenelle</ent>⟦br⟧
